Why CC BY-SA 4.0?

DAHAO is designed to be forked, modified, and shared. This license ensures:
1. Anyone can use and adapt DAHAO for their purpose
2. Improvements must be shared back with the community
3. Attribution maintains connection to the original work
4. Commercial use is permitted (enabling real-world adoption)

This aligns with @fork_freedom and @transparency principles.
